duties_responsibilities.duty: Generate & drive high-quality sales leads to assigned geographical area.

Utilize a variety of mediums to generate new memberships including nurturing productive relationships with senior citizens, partnering with external business partners such as health agents/ health brokers, key local community partners, and senior-focused businesses to enroll new patients into medical centers.

education_certification.credential: High School Diploma or GED required, associate's or bachelor’s degree preferred
